{"tid":2036790,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Bloomberg自己奶共就算，仲要公開屈李嘉誠的長和係「中資」！","createTime":"2020-05-26T16:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T18:11:40.000Z","uid":48040,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5b81f186945c11625357418adcd6e9d52df575a7","tid":2036790,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"Bloomberg奶共都幾出名，日日係度吹奏，中美貿易戰之中，中國一定係最大贏家，美國一定係輸家。現在又屈港資係中資，都唔知係唔係存心要矮化香港，令世界將港資同中資混為一談。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1590485475394&amp;issue=20200526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1590485475394%26issue%3D20200526&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=46b32c55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1590485475394&amp;issue=20200526</a><br />\n<br />\n據彭博報導，本港首富李嘉誠旗下的長和（0001）有份競投的以色列水廠項目已告落選，因為美國要求中東國家重新審視<span style=\"color: orange;\">中資為其帶來的潛在安全危機</span>。彭博未獲長和即時回覆置評要求。<br />\n<br />\n長和今次涉及的競標總值15億美元（約116.26億港元）Sorek B海水化淡廠項目。而美國國務卿Mike Pompeo在與以色列總理納坦雅胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）會面兩星期後，對和記水務入標一事表達關注。其後市場傳出，以色列當地官員在美國官員施壓下，最終可能影響長和在有關海水化淡廠的項目競標。<br />\n<br />\n=====<br />\n五毛話呢個channel的follower冇可能過一萬。你可以幫幫手嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_OtH-ee5lSw&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=d360003a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw</a>"},{"pid":"32f86d2801e966a0fa8a34b11120ba2459f6c3a4","tid":2036790,"uid":31237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:15:10.000Z","msg":"句野冇問題喎<br />\n的確係因為美國話要提防中資<br />\n佢先中唔到標"},{"pid":"e4e84508779d2171a49fc665cb555fc866a92f13","tid":2036790,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32f86d2801e966a0fa8a34b11120ba2459f6c3a4","tid":2036790,"uid":31237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:15:10.000Z","msg":"句野冇問題喎<br />\n的確係因為美國話要提防中資<br />\n佢先中唔到標"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:16:57.000Z","msg":"睇你點演繹。北京地震都可以話係龍氣太旺要爆發。"},{"pid":"f53d1c3d3c88c5d0c3c0cf7461d33cd6274c5da2","tid":2036790,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:17:13.000Z","msg":"咁香港又真係中國 吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413d1077e69a884177e22a9824504a36875c0dd6","tid":2036790,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f53d1c3d3c88c5d0c3c0cf7461d33cd6274c5da2","tid":2036790,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:17:13.000Z","msg":"咁香港又真係中國 吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:19:08.000Z","msg":"如果恆隆被標籤係中資，就可喜可賀。長和被標籤，就要為誠哥抱不平。"},{"pid":"d54265057184407933ec07ec640983e9b3026666","tid":2036790,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:24:24.000Z","msg":"其實呢，長和前身和黃已經一直係比美國當係中資<br />\n 巴拿馬運河當年已經嘈到好勁，而家就一定更加當佢係中資<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_560000/newsid_564400/564423.stm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2Fchinese%2Ftrad%2Fhi%2Fnewsid_560000%2Fnewsid_564400%2F564423.stm&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=29601385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_560000/newsid_564400/564423.stm</a>"},{"pid":"eee19959ff8ed16fa4266d84c42ecf095b48eb98","tid":2036790,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d54265057184407933ec07ec640983e9b3026666","tid":2036790,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:24:24.000Z","msg":"其實呢，長和前身和黃已經一直係比美國當係中資<br />\n 巴拿馬運河當年已經嘈到好勁，而家就一定更加當佢係中資<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_560000/newsid_564400/564423.stm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=